fu.util

Class IntIntervals

  • java.lang.Object
    • fu.util.IntIntervals

  • public class IntIntervals
extends java.lang.Object
    Intervals are a set of [from_i...to_i], where each number is an int.

        public static IntIntervals union(IntIntervals ints1,

        Computes the union set of two interval sets. The result contains those numbers that are at least in one of the sets.

      • difference

        public static IntIntervals difference(IntIntervals ints1,

        Computes the difference set of two interval sets. The result contains those numbers that are in the first set and not in the second set.
